## TypeShorts, 21 June 2012 in Brno ##

TypeShorts are an evening event full of short type presentations (exactly 321 seconds long) presented in a relaxed atmosphere of a café/wine cellar.

* **Date:** Thursday 21 June 2012, from ca 18:21
* **Place:** [Bistro Špargl](http://www.spargl.cz/), Gorkého 12, Brno ([map](http://maps.google.com/maps?q=Gork%C3%A9ho+12,+Brno-Veve%C5%99%C3%AD,+%C4%8Cesk%C3%A1+republika&hl=en&ie=UTF8&sll=37.0625,-95.677068&sspn=37.462243,78.574219&oq=gork%C3%A9ho+12&hnear=Gork%C3%A9ho+2%2F12,+602+00+Brno-Veve%C5%99%C3%AD,+Czech+Republic&t=m&z=16))
* **Entry fee:** first one registered pays 1 CZK, every other +1 CZK
